author: Paramount Plus
description:
A shuttle accident leaves Spock's (Ethan Peck) Vulcan DNA temporarily removed, turning him completely human just before a critical, ceremonial dinner with his fiancée T'Pring (Gia Sandhu) and her family. From a whole flood of new emotions to a sudden craving for bacon, watch Spock navigate the hilarious challenges of being human.

Stream Star Trek: Strange New Worlds on Paramount+.
